videos.headline: Wisconsin strikes first with Shaw's 21-yard TD run
videos.description: The Badgers are the first to get on the board when Bradrick Shaw gets through the line and zooms into the end zone from 21 yards away giving Wisconsin a 7-0 lead on Nebraska.

videos.headline: T. Armstrong Jr. pass intercepted, S. Shelton return  for 0 yds
videos.description: Tommy Armstrong Jr. pass intercepted Sojourn Shelton return for no gain to the Wisc 9

videos.headline: Ozigbo breaks through for Nebraska touchdown
videos.description: Facing a third-and-goal from the one, Nebraska finally gets into the end zone on Devine Ozigbo's one-yard run to tie the game at 7-7.

videos.headline: T. Armstrong Jr. pass intercepted, D. Dixon return  for 5 yds
videos.description: Tommy Armstrong Jr. pass intercepted D'Cota Dixon return for 5 yds to the 50 yard line

videos.headline: Wisconsin play-action works for 9-yard TD
videos.description: Wisconsin extends its lead in the third quarter when Alex Hornibrook keeps on the play-action and finds Robert Wheelwright for the touchdown to boost the Badgers up 17-7.

videos.headline: Armstrong caps 14-play drive with keeper TD run
videos.description: Nebraska finishes off a 14-play, 75-yard drive when Tommy Armstrong Jr. keeps on the read-option and makes a quick cut to stop a defender and get into the end zone cutting Wisconsin's lead to 17-14.

videos.headline: Nathan Gerry has his second interception of the 4th Quarter for Nebraska
videos.description: Bart Houston pass intercepted Nathan Gerry return for no gain to the Neb 30

videos.headline: Wisconsin misses a 45 yd Field Goal to take the lead with under 2 minutes left in the game
D. Ogunbowale run for 11 yds for a TD
videos.description: Dare Ogunbowale run for 11 yds for a TD

videos.headline: Wisconsin knocks down Nebraska's last gasp chance for win
videos.description: Needing a touchdown in overtime, Nebraska goes for it all on fourth down, but D'Cota Dixon is there to bat it away and win the game for Wisconsin.

videos.headline: Wisconsin hands Nebraska first loss of season with OT win
videos.description: Dare Ogunbowale's overtime touchdown is the difference maker as No. 11 Wisconsin upsets No. 7 Nebraska 23-17.
